### Test: Chained Response with Context (using previous_response_id) - V1 API
# This test demonstrates how to chain V1 responses together while maintaining context
# The model will have full context of the previous question and response without manually including it
# Expected Debug Headers:
# UAIG-Auth-Type: api-key
# UAIG-Selected-Backend: standard-responses-backend
# UAIG-Selected-API-Version: v1
# UAIG-API-Type: responses-v1 
# UAIG-Model-ID: gpt-4.1-mini
# UAIG-Forwarded-Path: /openai/v1/responses
